description: Robustness metrics along cost under CFA. Content is organized by : city name, type (static or dynamic), cut parameters (k, imbalance)/cuts pool size (n); every edge appearing at least one time in the cuts pool is ordered. Not displayed parameters are fixed to n=1000 (when k, imbalance vary), and k=2, imbalance=0.03 (when n varies). Robustness metrics include LCC metric (for the whole attack) and efficiency (until edge 150).
